{
  "script_id": "b-spline",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "设计字体、汽车曲面、动画路径，都需要又光滑又好控制的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "如果直接连点，线条会有生硬的折角，并不好看。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "数学家给出的答案之一，就是今天的主角——B 样条曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "control",
      "line_id": "ctrl-1",
      "filename": "control-ctrl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/control-ctrl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "我们先放下几个控制点，用虚线把它们连成控制多边形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "control",
      "line_id": "ctrl-2",
      "filename": "control-ctrl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/control-ctrl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "曲线并不穿过这些控制点，而是被它们像磁铁一样柔和地吸引。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "control",
      "line_id": "ctrl-3",
      "filename": "control-ctrl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/control-ctrl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "控制点决定曲线的大致走向，曲线却始终保持顺滑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-1",
      "filename": "basis-basis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "每个控制点都配一条基函数，作为它在各处的权重。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-2",
      "filename": "basis-basis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "这些基函数处处非负，且在每一点上求和恒等于一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "basis",
      "line_id": "basis-3",
      "filename": "basis-basis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/basis-basis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "关键在于：每条基函数只在一小段区间里不为零，这叫局部支撑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-1",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "贝塞尔曲线里，动一个控制点，整条曲线都会跟着变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-2",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "而 B 样条有局部支撑，改一个点只影响附近，远处纹丝不动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-3",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "这让 B 样条在处理很多控制点的复杂形状时得心应手。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "用鼠标拖动任意一个控制点，看曲线如何随之变形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "注意远端的曲线保持不动，这正是局部支撑的直观体现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "B 样条用控制点和基函数，拼出一条光滑可控的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "局部支撑让它比贝塞尔更灵活，是几何设计的基石。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "b-spline",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/b-spline/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "从字体到曲面，处处都有它的身影，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 34.82999999999999,
